      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  CommunityHalvesExpr
      A CommunitySetExpr that matches 32-bit community values via two separate CommunityHalfExpr matchers for the value's upper and lower 16-bits, retrievable via CommunityHalvesExpr.getLeft() and CommunityHalvesExpr.getRight() respectively.
